first_para: Steven Dominique Cheung (Chinese: 張敬龍) is the Liberal Democrats Candidate for Walthamstow  former Governor and Student Union President of City and Islington College, a British-Hongkonger broadcaster. London 2012 Young Mayor of the Olympic and Paralympic Village, Torch Bearer.

full.extract:
Steven Dominique Cheung (Chinese: 張敬龍) is the Liberal Democrats Candidate for Walthamstow  former Governor and Student Union President of City and Islington College, a British-Hongkonger broadcaster. London 2012 Young Mayor of the Olympic and Paralympic Village, Torch Bearer.
He was one of the youngest candidates who stood in the European Parliament elections on 4 June 2009.
full.title: Steven Dominique Cheung
